<font size=4>
<hr width="400" noshade>
<h2 align=center>Welcome to National Fuel!</h2>
<multicol cols=2>
<dd>In the year 2002, National Fuel will celebrate a significant milestone of business success - a century of outstanding service.
Our goal has always been to bring comfort, energy efficiency and a more rewarding way of life to our customers. At the same
time, we have maintained a sharp focus on the needs of our shareholders, employees and the natural gas industry. Our
history dates to the earliest days of the natural gas industry in the United States. We are also proud that we hold many
"industry firsts". <br>

<dd>We dedicate this World Wide Web site to that spirit and, in the coming months, hope to develop it into your destination for
information on National Fuel, the services we offer, energy saving measures, natural gas safety and the natural gas industry. 
</multicol>
<p>
<hr width="400" noshade>

